Package org.forgerock.openam.entitlement.indextree

Interface IndexChangeManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndexChangeManagerImpl
    public interface IndexChangeManager
    Responsible for ensuring all index changes are propagated to interested parties therefore keeping any index models up to date. The manager makes use of a IndexChangeObservable to notify interested parties of index changes. Any interested party needs to abide to the IndexChangeObserver contract and register with the manager.
    Author:
    andrew.forrest@forgerock.com
